§0The Great Chanadian Holocaust - By R509§0
§0
§01, The Players involved§0
§0
§0Kovio. Kovio is a complete faggot who dedicates >her life to 
#- spreading degeneracy and keeping everyone around >her poor, as seen by the ABR oligarcy, which is now§0
§0
§0De Facto instead of De Jure. Kovio is known to be against freedom of speech.§0
§0
§0R509. I lived through the Chanadan 
#- holocaust. My people were opressed under the trap administration. We were subjected to random pearlings, threats, and abuse by §0
§0
§0the government of Viridian. Ryan founded the famous Individualist Front, abbreviated to IDF. Ryan was a known 
#- proud /int/IS citizen, who stood against opression from Viridian. He would spend a week in the end without reason before his capturer set him§0
§0
§0free, when he would go flee to the wilderness for 2 weeks.§0
§0

#- NES2. NES2 is a friend of R509. NES and Ryan found out they had so much in common that NES merged his party, the CPP, into the IDF. NES and Ryan were through it all together.§0
§0
§0ChrisChrispie. Before becoming "Literally Judas", he was a fellow IDF member
#- who won seats in Intis. Chris has an obession with economics, commerce, and TRADE DEALS. He merged the Conservitive Party into the IDF.§0
§0
§0Prioma. She had fell inlove with NES2 in the most Autistic manor possible. She became 
#- crucial to the IDF as she was a high ranking political official in Viridian, which helped her to pull off 'The Ruse' (you will read about this later). §0
