§03. Details of NES2's Trial/The Ruse§0
§0
§0NES2 was put on Trial by Kovio. It was largely a witch trial, but NES2 was seen found innocent. NES2 was legally defended by Manabee, the best 
#- lawyer I've ever seen. Prioma, during the distraction of the trial§0
§0
§0dropchested the ABR's wealth to a secret loaction, where HGHG, just freed by Prioma, would take half the loot before giving the other half to me. HGHG would later submit to Kovio, telling
#- >her that I had the other half of the wealth. Kovio ransacked my §0
§0
§0little settlement, Priome. I was forced to give the wealth to Kovio and then left with a mess. This ransack lead to me heading north with NES2 and founding the 
#- short-lived country of Benistan.§0
§0
§04. Benistan§0
§0After the ruse, I headded North, North was far away from Chanada. I have become an exile. Me and NES2 created Benistan on a desolate island in the North. We made recruitment 
#- threads and managed to get a few Newfriends before it went downhill. §0
§0
§0Benistan went downhill when Kovio found out we were harboring an alt of Prioma (oops). So, without real proof or reason beforehand, we were chased out of 
#- Benistan, our town Ransacked. I went to Hjaltland, where I was quickly unwelcome. In an effort to get§0
§0
§0down to a Swamp NES said we'd flee to, I took the rail to Iria during the wee hours. I was found by a bounty hunter, whose name shall remain 
#- anonymous. He would later become one of my greatest friends and allies. My Pearl was held in the Bryn vault for a §0
§0
§0week or so, and apperantly I ate up 4 stacks of their coal during my time in the end. It was then that I would spend time up in 
#- the wilderness, away from civilization, a lone hermit. Later, I would strike a deal with HanTzu which provided me with a very§0
§0
§0kind freedom with a probation period until Febuary 2nd, though in effect Han was away from me and in Titan much sooner, de facto
#- ending my pribation period early. I logged on during late January to discover I've been banned from Chanada (again) in a purge§0
§0
§0of former revolutionaries, including ChrisChrispie. This lead me to 
#- Chanos, where I live today as I write this and continue to make and record History.§0

